description: Blanche`s Meowstic participated in the theme performance and free performance rounds of the Hiyoku Tripokalon Rookie Class Tournament. In the theme performance round, it managed to get the most votes and Blanche advanced but eliminated Serena. It performed with Blanche`s Meowstic in the free performance round but unfortunately their performance wasn`t good enough as Shauna won the tournament.
name: Nyaonix (Blanche)
